descriptionHtml:
Kman420\'s           

S-D-H-D-O-K-T-A-L      Mod
----------------------------------------


Super-Duper-HD-Ok-Thats-A-Lie   Mod
----------------------------------



Random Clutter Texture replacers  (Skyrim) (Texture Replacer) v1.0
-------------------------------------------------

Alternate higher res textures for lantern, bloody rags, workbench and cast iron pot\'s. All are brand new textures with new bumpmaps. Not 4096x4096, but way better than originals.



Installation
------------

Extract and move the textures folder to your skyrim/data folder - click \"yes to overwrite\" if necessary - it will only overwrite textures if you already have moded textures of these items.



Credits
-------

Kman420



Usage
-----

Please ask me before using in your own mod and also give me credit.



Kman420
